    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Businesses formed by one or more lawyers to engage in the practice of law, which entails advising and representing in civil or criminal law cases, business transactions, and other matters for which legal advice is required.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
